Reproducing Figures:
#SETUP:
In 02_data: put the gene position file created for the other folder (i.e Brain) named gene_position

#Analysis:

1) Rscript Figure_1_Table_gene_expression.R
2) Rscript Figures_1_to_4.R
3) Rscript Figure_5_6.R























